<link rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' href='blog.css'><script language='javascript' src='javascript/include.js'></script><h3>Write your letters now!</h3>
<div class='postDate'>Thursday, 27 April 2006</div>



<p class='postBody'>
 We've only got 1 (yes, that's <i>one</i>) letter to the editor for the upcoming Issue 3, so if you have feedback, whether positive or negative, please <a href="mailto:editor@prismmagazine.co.nz?subject=Letter%20to%20the%20editor">write in</a>.<br />
<br />
And if you want to be really helpful, ask all your friends what they thought of <a href="http://prismmagazine.co.nz/issue2/index.php">Issue 2</a> and see if they want to write some feedback. :-)
</p>

